thril Edged Short Sword in the primary and Long Sword of Ethereal Energy in the offhand. I was wondering if my damage output would increase or decrease if I replaced my Long Sword of Ethereal Energy with a Defenders Lightblade. The Defenders Lightblade is quite a bit slower, but has higher damage, especially when the magic damage of the LSoEE is resisted. Here are the stats of the three mentioned weapons if you don't recall them on the top off your head:<br>
<br>
Long Sword of Ethereal Energy <br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM <br>
